text: Libnan, a variant of Lubnan (Arabic), Lebanon (English) or Liban (French). Libnan may also refer to: *"Libnan" (Lydia Canaan song), 1993 *Ya Libnan, a Lebanese portal journalism ==See also== *Saydet Libnan, or Our Lady of Lebanon, a Marian shrine and a pilgrimage site in Lebanon
title: Libnan
